item.title: Episode 162 Audio: Ryan Grim
item.description: Over a year ago, Intercept journalists Ryan Grim and Murtaza Hussain broke a story that turned Pakistani politics upside down. The US had encouraged the Pakistani military establishment to oust Prime Minister Imran Khan, that country’s most popular politician.
